    ∇ path←SourcePath;source
    ⍝ Determine the source path of the class
     
      :Trap 6
          source←⍎'(⊃⊃⎕CLASS ⎕THIS).SALT_Data.SourceFile' ⍝ ⍎ works around a bug
      :Else
          :If 0=⍴source←{((⊃¨⍵)⍳⊃⊃⎕CLASS ⎕THIS)⊃⍵,⊂''}5177⌶⍬
              source←⎕WSID
          :Else ⋄ source←4⊃source
          :EndIf
      :EndTrap
      path←{(-⌊/(⌽⍵)⍳'\/')↓⍵}source
    ∇

